cs.NE, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.LG 

This paper deals with evolutionary algorithms, which are commonly used in the field of neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also focuses on combinatorial optimization problems, which fall under the category of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and distributed computing (cs.DC). Finally, the paper analyzes the speedup gained by parallelization, which is a topic of interest in machine learning and optimization (cs.LG).
